  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objectives are:

        -  To establish the prevalence of deep venous thrombosis through ultrasonography in
           Patients infected with COVID-19 admitted to hospital.

        -  To identify patients with higher risk of deep venous thrombosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
